author: dandiep
msg: Support lazy loading of bindings/transports/etc via SpringBeanMap. Now we read the BeanDefininition for the IDs/namespaces if they're there. If they aren't there, we resort to loading the bean and accessing them via getFooIds() (or getActivationNamespaces as it is in the Binding/Transport cases).
